Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:52.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0,0,0,,Au...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:53.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0,0,0,,Ešte stále ma to bolí.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.31,complete_25:05,Sign,0,0,0,,Dobyl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:59.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0,0,0,,"Vlajka-dobytia", však?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0,0,0,,Gao, Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0,0,0,,Od začiatku bolo veľa práce.
